prompt:
Patient: Hello?

Nurse: Hi, this is Rachel calling from O'Connor Hospital. I'm an AI on a recorded line. Is this Paxton Winner?

Patient: Yes. It is.

Nurse: Great, Mr. Winner. I'm calling about your upcoming total knee replacement. Is this a good time to talk?

Patient: Pretty good time to talk. Yes.

Nurse: I'm glad to hear that, Mr. Winner. How has your day been so far?

Patient: Not bad. Just you know,

responses.gpt4: That's nice to hear, Mr. Winner. Certainly, days leading up to a procedure can be a mixed bag of feelings. Are you managing to keep up with your usual routines despite the anticipation of the knee replacement?
responses.our_model: I'm glad to hear that, Mr. Winner. It's always good to have a day that's not bad. Is there anything in particular that's made your day better?
